snippet.title: Ratchet & Clank® Future: Quest for Booty Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/games/ratchet-and-clank/?emcid=or-1s-412983

The swashbuckling action in Ratchet & Clank® Future: Quest for Booty begins one year following the intense ending in Ratchet & Clank Future: Tools of Destruction®. Out now, exclusively through the PLAYSTATION®Network.

Ratchet and Clank Future:  Quest for Booty. ™/© 2008 SCEAI. Developed by Insomniac Games.
